      <title>上月注资 2,330 亿美元后，中国人民银行或将推迟下调存款准备金率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/pboc-seen-delaying-rrr-cut-after-adding-liquidity-via-new-tools</link>
